false,\"sortNumber\":0,\"amount\":0.0,\"remaining\":0.0,\"myHotelId\":0,\"fromDate\":\"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\"toDate\":\"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z\"},{\"id\":21677,\"accountId\":0,\"profileId\":0,\"agentId\":0,\"displayName\":\"6 - Abraj Al Hidayaa\",\"displayNumber\":null,\"isDefault\":false,\"isActive\":false,\"isDeleted\":false,\"isByAccount\":false,\"hasNoVat\":false,\"hasNoSaleVat\":false,\"isDisabled\":false,\"sortNumber\":0,\"amount\":0.0,\"remaining\":0.0,\"myHotelId\":0,\"fromDate\":\"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\"toDate\":\"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z\"},{\"id\":22571,\"accountId\":0,\"profileId\":0,\"agentId\":0,\"displayName\":\"7 - Abraj Al Hidayaa\",\"displayNumber\":null,\"isDefault\":false,\"isActive\":false,\"isDeleted\":false,\"isByAccount\":false,\"hasNoVat\":false,\"hasNoSaleVat\":false,\"isDisabled\":false,\"sortNumber\":0,\"amount\":0.0,\"remaining\":0.0,\"myHotelId\":0,\"fromDate\":\"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\"toDate\":\"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z\"}],\"reservationTags\":[],\"termsAndCondionList\":[{\"name\":\"Genral Policy\",\"details\":\"\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eAbove Rates are net \\u0026amp; non commision-able quoted in Saudi Riyals.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eAbove rates includes 15% Vat + 5% municipality.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eCheck in after 16:00 hours and check out at 12:00 hour.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eCheck in or check out amendment for individuals should be done 72\\u0026nbsp;hours prior to guest check in.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eCheck in or check out amendment for Group should be 7 days prior to guest check in.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eIn case of no-show for groups full amount will be charged.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eIn case of no-show for individuals first night will be charged.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eRight after confirmation, booking amendments, shouldn\\u0027t exceed 20% of total confirmed rooms.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eTriple and Quad occupancy will be provided with extra bed, If standard room is not available.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003ePAYMENT POLICY:\\u003cbr\\u003eGroups booking payment will be as follows:\\u003cbr\\u003e•\\u0026nbsp;\\u0026nbsp; \\u0026nbsp;%25 of total amount upon confirmation.\\u003cbr\\u003e•\\u0026nbsp;\\u0026nbsp; \\u0026nbsp;%25 of total amount has to be paid 21 days before each group arrival.\\u003cbr\\u003e•\\u0026nbsp;\\u0026nbsp; \\u0026nbsp;%50 of total amount has to be paid 14 days before each group arrival.\\u0026nbsp;\\u003cbr\\u003e•\\u0026nbsp;\\u0026nbsp; \\u0026nbsp;booking amendments, shouldn\\u0027t exceed 20% of total confirmed rooms.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"cancellationPolicyDetails\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eGroup reservations (5) rooms or more:\\u003cbr\\u003e•\\u0026nbsp;\\u0026nbsp; \\u0026nbsp;When cancelling after confirmation, 50% of the total amount including meals will be charged.\\u003cbr\\u003e•\\u0026nbsp;\\u0026nbsp; \\u0026nbsp;Less than 21 days before arrival, 25% of the total amount including meals will be charged.\\u003cbr\\u003e•\\u0026nbsp;\\u0026nbsp; \\u0026nbsp;Less than 14 days before arrival, 25% of the total amount including meals will be charged.\\u003cbr\\u003e•\\u0026nbsp;\\u0026nbsp; \\u0026nbsp;High season cancellation is subject to 100 % cancellation\\u0026nbsp;fee.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"nonRefundable\":false,\"hasFine\":true,\"isDefault\":true,\"id\":89},{\"name\":\"Train\",\"details\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003eTerms and Conditions\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003ePlease review all booking details carefully before confirming your reservation.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eGroup Reservations\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003col\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eStarts from 11 seats and above.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eLive train availabilities can\\u0027t be displayed or booked 4 days before the departure date.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003ePassengers details can\\u0027t be updated later than 4 Days from departure.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ol\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003ePayment Policy\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003ePayment must be completed via recharging your electronic wallet or by credit card advanced payment.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eGeneral Terms \\u0026amp; Conditions\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003col\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eEditing the reservation after payment is not available.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003ePassengers are allowed to carry:\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eOne small bag (handbag).\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eOne other piece not exceeding 25 kg. and not exceeding 65 x 55 x 35cm in terms of (length, width and height).\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eValid customer ID must be presented when travelling.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eBaggage check-in desks will open 2 hours before departure.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eBoarding gates will close 20 minutes before the stated departure time.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eIn case of issuing the tickets, All tickets are non-transferable and non-refundable, and can only be used by the named person on the ticket.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003ePassengers\\u0027 dress code onboard HHR trains must be in accordance to public dress code laws of KSA.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ol\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eChildren Policy\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003col\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eIn Economy Class:\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eChildren under 12 years are charged 50% of adult fare.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eInfants are charged 10% of the adult fare.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eIn Business Class:\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eChildren under 12 years are charged 60% of adult fare.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eInfants are charged 20% of the adult fare.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eInfants under 2 years will not occupy a separate seat.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ol\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eCancellation Policy\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003col\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003ePartial cancellation of reservation is not available.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eCancellations more than 20 days prior departure: Free of charge.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eCancellations from 20 to 7 days prior departure: 50% penalty of the ticket price.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eCancellations less than 7 days prior departure: 100% penalty.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eCancellations after ticket issuance is not available.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eFor Hajj bookings: 100% non-refundable. No cancellation is permitted under any circumstances\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ol\\u003e\",\"cancellationPolicyDetails\":\"\",\"nonRefundable\":false,\"hasFine\":true,\"isDefault\":false,\"id\":98},{\"name\":\"Ramadan\",\"details\":\"\\u003col\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eThe above rates are quoted in Saudi Riyals, net non-commissionable.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eNO CANCELLATION, NO AMENDMENT OR NO REFUND WILL BE ACCEPTED IN RAMADAN BOOKINGS.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eIn case of any Cancellation or Amendment No Refund will be made.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eCheck In 18:00 hrs. Check Out 12:00 hrs. One Full Night charged if guest check out after 12:00hrs.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eAll official documentations and rules to be followed.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eTriple or Quad occupancy will be through extra bed, If standard room is not available.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eThis Reservation should be guaranteed by cash\\u0026nbsp;\\u003cstrong\\u003eFULL\\u003c/strong\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;payment or voucher, other wise your reservation will be automatically released without any prior notice by the option date.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eAbove rates includes 15% Vat + 5% municipality.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ol\\u003e\",\"cancellationPolicyDetails\":\"\",\"nonRefundable\":false,\"hasFine\":false,\"isDefault\":false,\"id\":99},{\"name\":\"Visa\",\"details\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e1- Client Details: Full details of all clients, including passport copies, must be provided for visa processing.\\u003cbr\\u003e2- No Refund or Cancellation: Once a visa has been issued, no refunds or cancellations are allowed.\\u003cbr\\u003ePayment Terms:\\u003cbr\\u003e1- Payment must be made either from a floating deposit or via direct payment before the visa is issued.\\u003cbr\\u003e2- After confirmation, payment will be deducted from the floating deposit or made via direct payment.\\u003cbr\\u003e3- Any differences arising due to operational changes must be settled immediately after the end of each group transport.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e4- Above rates includes 15% Vat + 5% municipality.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eTransportation Services:\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e1- Pre-Invoice Issuance: A pre-invoice will be issued after receiving a transportation request.\\u003cbr\\u003e2- Invoice Review: The client must review the invoice within 24 hours of receipt.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"cancellationPolicyDetails\":\"\",\"nonRefundable\":false,\"hasFine\":false,\"isDefault\":false,\"id\":100},{\"name\":\"Hajj\",\"details\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e1- Above rates includes 15% Vat + 5% municipality.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e2- Above rates are based on the above mentioned meal plan.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e3- Above rates are per room per night.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e4- Above rates are net non-commissionable \\u0026amp; quoted in Saudi Riyals.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e5- In case of any cancellation or amendment no refund will be made as per Hajj policy. \\u0026nbsp;\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e6- Check in time is at 14:00 and Check out time is at 12:00,\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e7- any Stay above that will be Subject to hotel availability and extra Charges might be\\u0026nbsp;applied.\\u0026nbsp;\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"cancellationPolicyDetails\":\"\",\"nonRefundable\":false,\"hasFine\":false,\"isDefault\":false,\"id\":101},{\"name\":\"HANDLING\",\"details\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e- Above Rates are net \\u0026amp; non commission-able quoted in Saudi Riyals.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e- Above rates includes 15% Vat + 5% municipality.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e- In case of no-show 25% will be charged from the invoice value.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e- In case of High season (15th Dec till 07 Jan, Ramadan) 15% increase will be applied.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e- Indonesian-style meals box upon arrival at the airport According to Request With additional Charges.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;- Welcome kit: Company logo on the bus windows, Banner, Greeting card, and Snack box with your company logo can be provided with additional Charges.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eGround handling\\u003c/strong\\u003e is designed according to the default service standard to SAHL Indonesia as follows:\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e- Welcome drinks (Zamzam water 330ml, juice, water and dates) upon arrival.\\u003cbr\\u003e- Airport ground handling services on both arrival and departure.\\u003cbr\\u003e- Porter services at the airport (arrival \\u0026amp; departure).\\u003cbr\\u003e- Luggage weighing service (extra weight baggage fees not included).\\u003cbr\\u003e- Hotel check-in and check-out handling in both Makkah and Madinah.\\u003cbr\\u003e- Bellboy service to deliver luggage to the room door in Makkah and Madinah.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e- One snack during the Madinah Ziyarah tour per pax.\\u003cbr\\u003e- One snack during the Makkah Ziyarah tour per pax.\\u003cbr\\u003e- One snack on the Madinah–Makkah journey or vice versa per pax.\\u003cbr\\u003e- Four bottles of mineral water per pilgrim during the program.\\u003cbr\\u003e- 5 liters of Zamzam water for each pilgrim.\\u003cbr\\u003e- Operational support services: mutawwif/mutawwifah (religious guides), coordinators, and local representatives According to Request With additional Charges\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"cancellationPolicyDetails\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0026nbsp;Group reservations : • When cancelling after confirmation, 50% of the total amount will be charged. • Less than 21 days before arrival, 25% of the total amount \\u0026nbsp;will be charged. • Less than 14 days before arrival, 25% of the total amount \\u0026nbsp;will be charged. • High season cancellation is subject to 100 % cancellation fee.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"nonRefundable\":false,\"hasFine\":true,\"isDefault\":false,\"id\":129}],\"lookupVisaGroup\":null,\"lookupTransportationGroup\":null,\"lookupMOFAGroup\":null,\"isEditMode\":false,\"isSaleManager\":false,\"isSalesOfficer\":true,\"isClient\":false};\r\n\t</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n    <script type='text/javascript'>$(function($){});</script>\r\n\r\n    <script>\r\n        app.supportsTenancyNameInUrl = false;\r\n    </script>\r\n    <!--end::Page Snippets -->\r\n    <!--begin: svg symbols for alerts-->\r\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n        <symbol id=\"check-circle-fill\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\">\r\n            <path d=\"M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0zm-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z\" />\r\n        </symbol>\r\n        <symbol id=\"info-fill\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\">\r\n            <path d=\"M8 16A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16zm.93-9.412-1 4.705c-.07.34.029.533.304.533.194 0 .487-.07.686-.246l-.088.416c-.287.346-.92.598-1.465.598-.703 0-1.002-.422-.808-1.319l.738-3.468c.064-.293.006-.399-.287-.47l-.451-.081.082-.381 2.29-.287zM8 5.5a1 1 0 1 1 0-2 1 1 0 0 1 0 2z\" />\r\n        </symbol>\r\n        <symbol id=\"exclamation-triangle-fill\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 